1. *Pokazuje* nam put do njegovog doma. (It shows us the way to his house.)
2. Ona *pokazuje* svoju ljubav prema njemu. (She shows her love for him.)
3. Oni su *pokazivali* odlične rezultate u školi. (They were showing excellent results at school.)
4. Ona će *pokazati* svoje znanje. (She will show her knowledge.)
5. Oni su *pokazali* svoju podršku njenom projektu. (They showed their support for her project.)